0. Recipe for the impatient
---------------------------

The following should work on lxplus and elsewhere, both on 64bits and 32bits architecture
   cd SOMEWHERE
   scramv1 project CMSSW 1_6_8
   cd CMSSW_1_6_8/src
   eval `scramv1 runtime -csh`
   project CMSSW
   cvs co AnalysisDataFormats/HeavyFlavorObjects
   cvs co HeavyFlavorAnalysis/Examples
   cd AnalysisDataFormats/HeavyFlavorObjects/
   make all
   cd ../../HeavyFlavorAnalysis/Examples
   scramv1 b
   cd test
   
